General.Name: Dimension Computer Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: Dimension Computer Technology Co., Ltd. provides information management and system services primarily in Taiwan. The company offers consultancy, education training, manpower outsourcing, hardware integration planning and installation, repair service, and software sales and technical support services, as well as virtualization solutions and lotus coexistence and migration solutions. Dimension Computer Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Taipei, Taiwan.
General.Address: No. 147, Jianguo North Road, Taipei, Taiwan, 104
